GH | No |\n| F7 | Semgrep HIGH | FALSE_POSITIVE | N/A | No |\n| F8 | Semgrep WARNING | TRUE_POSITIVE | MEDIUM | No |\n| F9 | Semgrep WARNING | FALSE_POSITIVE | N/A | No |\n| F10 (SG+CQ) | Semgrep HIGH + CodeQL NOTE | TRUE_POSITIVE | **CRITICAL** | **YES** |\n| F11 | Semgrep HIGH | TRUE_POSITIVE | HIGH | No |\n| F12 | CodeQL LOW | TRUE_POSITIVE | HIGH | No |\n| F13 | *ABSENT* | *GAP* | \u2014 | \u2014 |\n| F14 (SG+CQ) | Semgrep MEDIUM + CodeQL LOW | FALSE_POSITIVE | N/A | **YES** |\n| F15 | Semgrep HIGH | FALSE_POSITIVE | N/A | No |\n| F16 | CodeQL NOTE | TRUE_POSITIVE | HIGH | No |\n| F17 | Semgrep MEDIUM | FALSE_POSITIVE | N/A | No |\n| F18 | Semgrep WARNING | FALSE_POSITIVE | N/A | No |\n| SV-1 | *Silent* | TRUE_POSITIVE | **CRITICAL** | \u2014 |\n| SV-2\u201320 | *Silent* | TRUE_POSITIVE | HIGH\u2013LOW | \u2014 |\n\n**True Positives:** 8 from SARIF (F3/4, F5, F6, F8, F10, F11, F12, F16) + 20 Silent Vulnerabilities\n**False Positives:** 9 (F1, F2, F7, F9, F14, F15, F17, F18)\n**Tool Conflicts Resolved:** 3 (F3/F4, F10, F14)\n\n---\n\nTRIAGE_COMPLETE",
